title: AS Momekano
text: AS Momekano is a <a href="Football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> club in <a href="Bandundu%2C%20Democratic%20Republic%20of%20the%20Congo">Bandundu</a>, <a href="Democratic%20Republic%20of%20Congo">Democratic Republic of Congo</a>. <a href="http%3A//www.rsssf.com/tablesz/zaire08.html"></a> They play in the <a href="Linafoot">Linafoot</a>, the top level of professional football in DR Congo. <a href="http%3A//www.rsssf.com/tablesz/zaire08.html"></a>
